---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: John Blake - NLP Research
quote: '"Grit, tenacity and perseverance outweigh talent." — John Blake'
---

<section class="page-header">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>John Blake</h1>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="profile-layout">
      <div class="profile-text">
        <div class="profile-photo-wrap">
          <img src="{{ '/assets/JB_2025c.png' | url }}" alt="John Blake" class="profile-photo" id="dynamicImage">
        </div>
        <p class="lead">I am a multidisciplinary researcher with degrees in applied linguistics, education, computer science, mathematics education, business administration, creative writing, and combined studies. Much of my work is at the intersection of natural language processing (NLP) and forensic linguistics, with a particular focus on authorship analysis, including attribution, verification, and profiling. I develop software and online tools that make linguistic analysis more systematic, transparent, and applicable to real-world problems. I am particularly interested in combining corpus-based approaches with machine learning and explainable AI. My broader research agenda includes computational stylistics, cross-genre and cross-modal authorship analysis, and the design of intelligent systems for language analysis and learning. I lead and collaborate on projects that translate theoretical insights into practical tools, with an emphasis on usability, interpretability, and impact.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="profile-demo">
        <div class="demo-card">
          <label for="demo-input" class="form-label fw-semibold mb-2">
            <i class="bi bi-chat-square-text me-2"></i>Sentiment Analysis Demo
          </label>
          <textarea id="demo-input" class="form-control mb-3" placeholder="Type or paste any text here... (e.g., 'I love learning new things!' or 'This is frustrating.')"></textarea>
          <button id="analyze-btn" class="btn btn-primary w-100">
            <i class="bi bi-cpu me-2"></i>Analyse Sentiment
          </button>
          <div id="result-container" class="result-container"></div>
          <p class="text-muted small mt-3 mb-0">
            <i class="bi bi-info-circle me-1"></i>Powered by Transformers.js - runs entirely in your browser
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="py-5">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row g-4 section-cards">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card section-card h-100">
          <div class="card-body text-center">
            <i class="bi bi-journal-richtext card-icon"></i>
            <h3 class="card-title">Research</h3>
            <p class="card-text text-muted">Publications, projects, and opportunities for graduate students interested in NLP and computational linguistics.</p>
            <a href="{{ '/research/' | url }}" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Explore Research</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card section-card h-100">
          <div class="card-body text-center">
            <i class="bi bi-app-indicator card-icon"></i>
            <h3 class="card-title">Tools</h3>
            <p class="card-text text-muted">Educational web applications, datasets, and tools for language learning and text analysis.</p>
            <a href="{{ '/tools/' | url }}" class="btn btn-outline-primary">View Tools</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="card section-card h-100">
          <div class="card-body text-center">
            <i class="bi bi-mortarboard card-icon"></i>
            <h3 class="card-title">Courses</h3>
            <p class="card-text text-muted">Online course materials covering academic writing, language patterns, and computational methods.</p>
            <a href="{{ '/courses/' | url }}" class="btn btn-outline-primary">Browse Courses</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% block scripts %}
<script type="module" src="{{ '/assets/js/sentiment.js' | url }}"></script>
<script defer src="{{ '/assets/js/photo-swap.js' | url }}"></script>
{% endblock %}
